ion for ABC Studios in California. His work as an author has gained attention in the UK and his first children\'s book \"Lillee Can Be\" has been released in London. It is a Gender Equality book encouraging young girls to surpass preconceived expectations about their gender. For more information about it, check out the promotional video on Youtube. Simply type \"Lillee Can Be\" into the search bar. \"Lillee Can Be\" is available as paperback and e-book at Waterstones in England, Hodges Figgis in Ireland, Bokus in Sweden, Barnes & Noble in the US, and Amazon internationally. He is enjoying his unanticipated success as an author and he has many more books to come! He looks forward to every unexpected endeavor and relishes each experience to the fullest. As always, he thanks his mother for all of her support and is excited to support her on all of her endeavors. He is estranged from his father and much of his paternal extended family with no interest in reconciliation. Aside from all things creative, Adam adores animals and wildlife, and has a particular affinity for ferrets. Live life to the fullest and never be afraid to stare down an obstacle because there is nothing but greatness on the other side.<br>\n         ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'7662127','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjY1ZWViNzAtZTE0Mi00ODAxLWE4MmUtYTAyZjRmMTVlNGQ2XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjMyNzIwOTE@._V1_UY317_CR16,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(589,'Natalie Pellegrino',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'9320112',NULL,0),(590,'Robert Shropshire',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'4741866',NULL,0),(591,'Marcelo Martinessi',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'3308584',NULL,0),(592,'Hilde Berg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'0073783',NULL,0),(593,'Tito Cabrera Vendeuvre',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'0092560',NULL,0),(594,'Agustina Chiarino',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1887162',NULL,0),(595,'Fernando Epstein',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'0258459',NULL,0),(596,'Christoph Friedel',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'0295016',NULL,0),(597,'Júlia Murat',NULL,NULL,NULL