 as best young actor in 1989. In the early nineties Marx plays in TV productions a lot, e.g. in \'Die Tote von Amelung\' and in \'Mörderische Zwillinge\', though without completely abandoning to work on stage. He tours with Schiller\'s \'Die Räuber\', plays at the theater in Düsseldorf and at Berlin\'s Volksbühne. After 1996 Marx increasingly appears in TV serials, e.g. in \'Die Drei\', \'Tatort\', \'Balko, der Clown\', and \'SoKo 5113\'. In 2000 he plays the main role in the TV movie \'Die Wunde\'. In \'Dark Blue World\' he plays a sergeant for cinema, and in the cinema feature \'Freie Tanke\' (2000) he is one of the leads. In 2003 Horst-Günter Marx plays the role of Josef Mattis in the screen play \'Milchwald\' (Le bois lacte). In 2006 he appeared in the BBC documentary \'Auschwitz\', playing the role of KZ-commander Rudolf Höss. Horst-Günter Marx is currently playing lead in the German TV series \'Tierärztin Dr. Mertens\'.<br>\n         ','1955-12-01 00:00:00',NULL,'Caputh, German Democratic Republic','0555620','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjAzOTEyMjUzMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNzcxNjQzNA@@._V1_UX214_CR0,0,214,317_AL_.jpg',1545843479),(761,'Laila Maria Witt',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2982880',NULL,0),(762,'Adriana Altaras',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'0022672',NULL,0),(763,'Lena Binski',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'9340309',NULL,0),(764,'Silvina Buchbauer',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'0118108',NULL,0),(765,'Tania Carlin',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'5293787',NULL,0),(766,'Illia Chaikovskyi',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'8120656',NULL,0),(767,'Ruth Gumpel',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'9253912',NULL,0),(768,'Eugen Herman-Friede',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1890299',NULL,0),(769,'Pamela Knaack',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'0460398',NULL,0),(770,'Tobias Lauterberg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'0491604',NULL,0),(771,'Ulrike Lodwig',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2337146',NULL,0),(772,'Hanni Lévy',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'9253911',NULL,0),(773,'Theresa Schneider',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'77764